Orange – Restrict 
 1) Implement enhanced measures, restrictions and enforcement avoiding any closures.

Title: Control
Description:
Red – Control 
 1) Implement broader-scale measures and restrictions, across multiple sectors, to control transmission. 
 2) Restrictions are the most severe available before widescale business or organizational closure.

Title: Lockdown
Description:
Grey – Lockdown 
 1) Implement widescale measures and restrictions, including closures, to halt or interrupt transmission. 
 2) Consider declaration of emergency.

Title: Lockdown
Description:
ONTARIO REGULATION 11/21 
 made under the EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT AND CIVIL PROTECTION ACT
